newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,756 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,756 contracts.

text.p: The Chicago Board of Trade Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totalled 1,756 contracts compared with 2,060 the previous session, according to the CBOT.
There were 143 wheat, 1,302 corn, 300 soybean, 1 soymeal, 3 oat, 3 corn calls, 3 corn puts and one soybean call traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 1/4 cent per bushel higher to one cent lower, corn was one to 1/2 cent higher and soybeans were 4-1/2 cents higher to 1/2 cent lower.
